title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of sync (1GILQD5)
description: The current implementation of JarExporter is causing out of sync issues (1GILQD5). The exported jar file includes itself, which is likely causing the problem.
OB: The application becomes out of sync after exporting a jar file using the JarExporter.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself to prevent out of sync issues.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Export a jar file using the JarExporter. 
2. Run the exported jar file in the application. 
3. Observe that the application becomes out of sync.
